# How to Change the apache port in cpanel


1. Go to WHM
1. Click on tweak settings
1. click on System tab
1. Find, "Apache non-SSL IP/Port"
1. And enter 0.0.0.0:81

Then restart apache


```
# service httpd restart
```

You can change 81 to any other port which you would like to change for apache.
